sql_statement.static: select

as deviceCount, Sb.PercentageLoad AS 'ILoad', Sb.MbpsLoad AS 'OLoad', TxEotStreamResults.FrameCount as TxFramecount, RxEotStreamResults.SigFrameCount as RxFramecount, 0 as LPortFloodCount, 0 as TPortFloodCount, 0 as MPortFloodCount, 'fail' as IterationResult from TxEotStreamResults, RxEotStreamResults, Port, Streamblock as Sb where RxEotStreamResults.StreamIndex = TxEotStreamResults.StreamIndex and RxEotStreamResults.PortName = Port.Name and Port.Id != 3 and TxEotStreamResults.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle

Children.Name: If

sql_for_command_verdict.static: SELECT CASE COUNT(*) WHEN 0 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END
FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' AND name='Rfc2889CachingMPort'

sql_statement.static: DROP TABLE IF EXISTS Rfc2889CachingMPort
select RxEotStreamResults.SigFrameCount as RxCount from RxEotStreamResults, Port where RxEotStreamResults.PortName = Port.Name and Port.Id = 3

Children.Name: Update Monitor: Run SQL Command 24

sql_statement.static: UPDATE Rfc2889CachingIterationTemp SET MPortFloodCount = (select RxCount from Rfc2889CachingMPort) WHERE Rfc2889CachingIterationTemp.rowid = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Rfc2889CachingIterationTemp)

report_verdict.passed_verdict_explanation: Number of frames detected by the Learning port was equal to the frames sent by Test port AND no frames were detected by the Monitor port.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE IterationResult WHEN 'fail' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END FROM Rfc2889CachingIterationTemp WHERE Rfc2889CachingIterationTemp.rowid = (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Rfc2889CachingIterationTemp)

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Number of frames detected by the Learning port was not equal to the frames sent by Test port OR frames were detected by the Monitor port.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN count(*) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END from (select OLoad from Rfc2889CachingIteration where LPortFloodCount = 0 and TPortFloodCount = 0 and MPortFloodCount = 0 and TxFramecount = RxFramecount)

sql_statement.static: select

as 'Configured Traffic Rate Threshold (%)', case when OLoad > 0 then OLoad else 'N/A' END as 'Offered Load (Mbps)', case when max(deviceCount) > 0 then max(deviceCount) else 'N/A' END as 'Maximum Cached Addresses' from Rfc2889CachingIteration where LPortFloodCount = 0 and TPortFloodCount = 0 and MPortFloodCount = 0  and TxFramecount = RxFramecount
